            <div class="prog-body">
              Courses covering digital transformation navigation, productivity tools,
              data literacy, cybersecurity practices, and mechatronics for Industry 4.0 —
              equipping professionals for the smart manufacturing era.
            </div>
            <div class="prog-duration"><i class="fi fi-rr-clock"></i> 8 – 200 Hours</div>
          </div>

