            <div class="prog-body">
              A suite of curriculum-aligned mobile apps that transform review sessions into
              game-like experiences. Supports formative assessment, remedial learning, and
              consistent student engagement for basic education.
            </div>
            <div class="prog-duration"><i class="fi fi-rr-clock"></i> Self-Paced</div>
          </div>

          <div class="prog-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
            <div class="prog-num">Program 05</div>
            <div class="prog-icon"><i class="fi fi-rr-trophy"></i></div>
            <div class="prog-title">Robotics, AI &amp; Academic Drone Challenges</div>
            <div class="prog-body">
              An annual national event — the Philippine Robotics Cup — where students showcase
              skills in robotics assembly, coding, AI problem-solving, and drone soccer,
              fostering innovation and STEM excellence nationwide.
            </div>
            <div class="prog-duration"><i class="fi fi-rr-calendar"></i> Annual Event</div>
