              plus TESDA-accredited courses: Mechatronics Servicing NC&nbsp;II (158 hrs) and
              Electronics Back-End Operation NC&nbsp;II (80 hrs).
            </div>
            <div class="prog-duration"><i class="fi fi-rr-clock"></i> 80 – 158 Hours</div>
